data.description: WELCOME TO LUXURY...This beautiful open concept home located in a quiet Estrella Mountain Ranch neighborhood offers plenty of room with 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms + den. Granite countertops throughout and stainless kitchen appliances. Backyard features include an inviting heated pool with a relaxing spa and fire pots to light up the night. Great for entertaining, and for enjoying your quiet oasis with family and friends. Surrounding community offers two lakes with paved walking paths, multiple parks, community pools, waterslide and splash pads, basketball courts, pickleball, tennis, and miles & miles of hiking and biking trails...Welcome Home.
